  "body": "### Metadata\r\n\r\n* **Hardfork**: frontier\r\n\r\n### What was wrong?\r\n\r\nThe spec doesn't ensure that the `parent_hash` of the current block matches the hash of the previous block.\r\n\r\n### Sources\r\n\r\n> **parentHash**: The Keccak 256-bit hash of the parent block’s header, in its entirety; formally H<sub>p</sub>.\r\n\r\n[source](https://ethereum.github.io/yellowpaper/paper.pdf#subsection.4.3)\r\n",
